+## import chatgpt-export
+
+Imports ChatGPT export files into local memory records.
+
+Supported inputs:
+
+| Input | Behavior |
+|---|---|
+| `.zip` | Reads supported text files inside the archive |
+| folder | Recursively imports supported files |
+| `.json` | Parses ChatGPT conversation mappings when present |
+| `.html` / `.htm` | Extracts visible text |
+| `.md` / `.txt` | Imports raw text |
+
+```text
+python pala.py import chatgpt-export export.zip
+```
+
+Useful options:
+
+| Option | Purpose |
+|---|---|
+| `--project trugurpala/pala-memory-core` | Link imported records to a project |
+| `--tag archive` | Add an extra tag |
+| `--max-records 25` | Limit created records |
+| `--max-chars 12000` | Limit text stored per record |
+
 ## dashboard serve
 
 Starts a local dashboard server from the `dashboard/` folder.
