+## ChatGPT Export Import Behavior
+
+The first ChatGPT export connector reads local files only. It supports `.zip`, folders, `.json`, `.html`, `.md`, and `.txt`.
+
+| Input | Behavior |
+|---|---|
+| ChatGPT-style `mapping` JSON | Splits conversations into memory records |
+| Other JSON | Stores formatted JSON as one record |
+| HTML | Extracts visible text |
+| Markdown/Text | Stores text directly |
+
 ## Design Rule
 
 If a connector is fragile, keep it optional. The core should still work through manual capture and file import.
